info.name: Cabildo
info.description:
DESIGN BY:
Eric Solé

MATERIALS:
Body lamp in painted die-cast aluminium. The indirect light shapes the body lamp, bringing out its winding form and giving it the astonishing appearance of a ring of light. The suspension cables are also feed cables.

INFORMATIONS:
HALO max1x230W (R7s) – ECOn
Dimmable
